sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Any Webview
participant Router as MessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as Feature Use Case
participant Policy as SemanticActionPolicy
participant PlanRegistry as OperationPlanRegistry
participant Validator as GuardAcknowledgementValidator
participant Worktree as Worktree implements WorktreeOperationCapabilities
participant Runtime as GitRuntime

User->>App: Request guarded action
App->>Router: guarded action request(worktreeLocator, actionInput, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>UseCase: prepare(Worktree, actionInput, signal)
UseCase->>Policy: guardsFor(semanticAction)
Policy-->>UseCase: OperationGuard list
UseCase->>UseCase: Build targets, preview, and recovery hints
UseCase-->>Router: OperationPlan
Router->>PlanRegistry: store(OperationPlan, Worktree)
PlanRegistry-->>Router: stored OperationPlan
Router-->>App: operation plan response(requestId, OperationPlan)
App-->>User: Show guards and preview

User->>App: Acknowledge guards
App->>Router: guarded action execute(worktreeLocator, actionInput, GuardAcknowledgement, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>Validator: validate(GuardAcknowledgement, Worktree)
Validator->>PlanRegistry: get(planId)
PlanRegistry-->>Validator: OperationPlan
alt acknowledgement is valid
  Validator-->>Router: validated acknowledgement
  Router->>UseCase: execute(Worktree, actionInput, validated acknowledgement, signal)
  UseCase->>Worktree: semantic action(signal)
  Worktree->>Runtime: execute(operation, executionContext, input, signal)
  Runtime-->>Worktree: result
  Worktree-->>UseCase: result
  UseCase-->>Router: result
  Router->>PlanRegistry: expire(planId)
  Router-->>App: guarded action response(requestId, result)
else acknowledgement is invalid, stale, or expired
  Validator-->>Router: validation error
  Router-->>App: error(requestId, invalid acknowledgement)
end
